snippet.title: Mooshie's Kitchen 2 - Indie Horror Game - No Commentary
snippet.description:
Thanks For Watching!

Facebook https://www.facebook.com/Stella-Abbasi-100150965166877/
Twitter https://twitter.com/StellaAbbasi

Mooshie's Kitchen 1 Video: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=aV6Aue3F9gg&t=738s

Download https://omogonixlachlan.itch.io/mooshies-kitchen-2

Welcome back to Mooshie's Kitchen! Things have changed since you were last here...

In Mooshie's Kitchen 2, you play as Todd once again. After escaping Mooshie's, Todd is approached by the FBI and the US government to go back to Mooshie's Kitchen on a top-secret black operations mission to stop Mooshie once and for all! If Todd succeeds, he'll be given tax-exempt status and will never have to pay taxes in his life again!

Indie Horror Game Playlist https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLk0tZ0YT3FZEsIgd3Qdj19xGe9VcMMI1P

#mooshieskitchen #Indiegames
